OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening, mostly dry but a few patches
OL,7,Fof rain. Later this evening and
OL,8,Fovernight some heavier outbreaks of
OL,9,Frain are likely, with a southerly
OL,10,Fbreeze picking up. Mild and rather
OL,11,Fhumid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy rain. Becoming
OL,15,Fdrier later with some bright spells
OL,16,Facross Tayside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
