OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fclears north Saturday morning to leave
OL,7,Fthe afternoon and Sunday dry and
OL,8,Fbright, and becoming warm. Monday
OL,9,Fstaying dry with some sunshine.
